    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 36.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第36课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Across the Channel.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "横渡海峡。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "First listen and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "What is Debbie going to try to do?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "黛比准备尝试做什么？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Debbie Hart is going to swim across the English channel tomorrow.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "黛比·哈特明天准备游过英吉利海峡。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "She is going to set out from the French coast at five o'clock in the morning.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她准备清晨五点从法国海岸出发。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "Debbie is only 11 years old and she hopes to set up a new world record.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "黛比只有11岁，她希望创下一项新的世界纪录。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "She is a strong swimmer and many people feel that she is sure to succeed.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她游泳很棒，许多人认为她一定会成功。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Debbie's father will set out with her in a small boat.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "黛比的父亲将乘一条小船和她一起出发。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "Mr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "哈特"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "Hart has trained his daughter for years.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先生训练女儿已经多年。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "Tomorrow he will be watching her anxiously as she swims the long distance to England.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "明天，当她长途游向英国时，他将焦急地注视着她。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "Debbie intends to take short rests every two hours.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "黛比打算每两小时短暂休息一次。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "She will have something to drink but she will not eat any solid food.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她会喝些东西，但不吃任何固体食物。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "Most of Debbie's school friends will be waiting for her on the English coast.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "黛比的大多数同学将在英国海岸等候她。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "Among them will be Debbie's mother, who swam the channel herself when she was a girl.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "其中还有黛比的母亲，她年轻时也曾游过英吉利海峡。"
      }
    }
  ],
